<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>Caption</tag> is an extended description of a <tag>MediaObject</tag>.
Unlike a <tag>TextObject</tag>, which is an alternative to the other elements
in the <tag>MediaObject</tag>, the <tag>Caption</tag> augments the 
object.
